1
00:00:14,880 --> 00:00:15,480
Huainan.

2
00:00:16,079 --> 00:00:18,080
This jade pendant is unique.

3
00:00:18,240 --> 00:00:20,040
The quality and carving are excellent.

4
00:00:20,040 --> 00:00:22,300
It goes perfectly with my new cheongsam.

5
00:00:22,480 --> 00:00:23,480
Can I have it?

6
00:00:23,720 --> 00:00:25,520
You want something that belonged to the dead?

7
00:00:25,520 --> 00:00:27,520
If you like it, take it, Stepmother.

8
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:33,610
Where is Shengsheng? Where did she go?

9
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:35,240
Just after you left,

10
00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:36,920
she went out.

11
00:00:37,560 --> 00:00:38,360
Stepmother,

12
00:00:38,360 --> 00:00:40,600
your status isn't what it used to be.

13
00:00:40,920 --> 00:00:41,920
Watch your step.

14
00:00:42,320 --> 00:00:44,760
If you make things hard for her like last time...

15
00:00:44,760 --> 00:00:46,760
Don't blame me for being heartless.

16
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:47,730
Understood.

17
00:00:48,080 --> 00:00:49,400
I have to go to the military headquarters.

18
00:00:49,400 --> 00:00:50,860
I'll be back late tonight.

19
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:52,360
When she gets here, tell her

20
00:00:52,360 --> 00:00:53,360
not to wait for me.

21
00:00:54,680 --> 00:00:55,200
Wait.

22
00:00:56,440 --> 00:00:57,970
Your clothes are wrinkled.

23
00:01:00,360 --> 00:01:01,960
Yao Shengsheng is really unbelievable.

24
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:04,040
You are a great general who fights in wars.

25
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:05,880
It's not like you're a scholar.

26
00:01:05,880 --> 00:01:08,280
I'll keep this fountain pen for you for now.

27
00:01:29,800 --> 00:01:31,130
What are you doing here?

28
00:01:31,160 --> 00:01:32,160
Long story short,

29
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,800
Song Huainan gave the jade pendant to Yuemei.

30
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:35,600
Also, the bug was likely found.

31
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:37,200
It's dangerous for you to go back.

32
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:39,000
But the jade pendant is still at the Song house.

33
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:41,130
I have to go back, no matter the danger.

34
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:50,720
Doesn't this suit my complexion?

35
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:51,400
Try it.

36
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:51,840
Okay.

37
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,039
What perfume is this?

38
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,330
The scent is subtle.

39
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:57,570
But the rich fragrance feels like clearing the mist.

40
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:58,520
This?

41
00:01:59,039 --> 00:02:01,560
The Master specially asked someone

42
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:03,730
to bring it back from France for me.

43
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:06,560
I'll ask Huainan to buy me a bottle someday.

44
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,259
No need to bother Huainan.

45
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:12,520
I have everything here.

46
00:02:12,920 --> 00:02:14,000
What do you like?

47
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:15,680
I'll give it to you.

48
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,640
Your jewelry

49
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:19,040
looks really nice.

50
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:24,079
But the style is a bit old-fashioned.

51
00:02:24,079 --> 00:02:25,440
Old-fashioned.

52
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:26,840
How is it old-fashioned?

53
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:29,280
You really have high standards.

54
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:31,920
Why don't you show us something,

55
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:33,000
so we can see

56
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:35,000
what isn't old-fashioned?

57
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:37,520
And broaden our horizons.

58
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:38,800
How could I carry precious items

59
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,280
around with me casually?

60
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,240
However,

61
00:02:42,480 --> 00:02:44,360
there is something I really like,

62
00:02:44,920 --> 00:02:46,920
but sadly, I never managed to buy it.

63
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:49,040
I still feel it's a pity.

64
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,240
What is it?

65
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,040
A jade pendant.

66
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:55,680
The jade was exquisite and finely carved.

67
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,480
It looked truly extraordinary.

68
00:02:57,760 --> 00:03:00,040
It's just a jade pendant.

69
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:03,200
I have plenty of those.

70
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:08,520
Huainan even gave me one today.

71
00:03:08,880 --> 00:03:10,960
I think it's just so-so.

72
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,200
Nothing special.

73
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,820
Huainan gave you one, too?

74
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:17,370
Impossible.

75
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:19,440
Why would Huainan give you anything?

76
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:22,440
Believe it or not, it was a gift from Huainan.

77
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:25,840
I just put it away.

78
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,240
I didn't bring it with me.

79
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,640
I'll show it to you another time.

80
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:37,440
It's dirty.

81
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:38,370
My hand slipped.

82
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:41,090
Your clothes are all dirty.

83
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:43,640
I'll take you to change into something new.

84
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:44,840
No need, Stepmother.

85
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,560
Huainan gave me plenty of clothes.

86
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:48,160
I'll just go back and change.

87
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,490
Enjoy your chat.

88
00:03:58,160 --> 00:04:00,120
The jade pendant given to Yuemei,

89
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:02,820
could it be the one I've been looking for?

90
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:10,300
Song Qingzhou.

91
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:12,090
What do you want?

92
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:13,920
Why don't I take you to change

93
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:15,200
into some clean clothes?

94
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:16,800
No need. I can change at home.

95
00:04:17,880 --> 00:04:18,560
Is that so?

96
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,880
Why do you have my pen?

97
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:26,080
I picked it up.

98
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,280
Yuemei came out of your room

99
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:29,880
and threw it in the trash can.

100
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:32,010
Where are you taking me?

101
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,840
I want to confirm something.

102
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:44,040
Hello. Welcome.

103
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,360
This way, please.

104
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,280
How is it?

105
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:27,920
Do you like it?

106
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:57,330
Such a beautiful diamond necklace

107
00:05:57,440 --> 00:05:59,320
needs a beautiful dress to match.

108
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:02,460
Come on.

109
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:04,720
Go try it on.

110
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:09,560
What's wrong?

111
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:11,080
Don't you like it?

112
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:13,420
I picked this out especially for you.

113
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,850
You are Rose, right?

114
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,240
Of course.

115
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:31,880
Then do you know Yao Shengsheng?

116
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:33,900
Who are you?

117
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:37,960
Yao Shengsheng is married to Song Huainan now.

118
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:39,760
I am his brother, Song Qingzhou.

119
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:41,600
As for you,

120
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:44,860
you were Yao Shengsheng's friend for years.

121
00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:46,400
Because your family was poor,

122
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:48,520
you always played second fiddle to her.

123
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:49,600
To support your family,

124
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:51,860
you had to secretly work here as a dancer.

125
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:55,000
And that rich young boyfriend who chased you back then

126
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,080
dumped you

127
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:58,159
to pursue Yao Shengsheng instead, right?

128
00:06:58,159 --> 00:06:59,090
What do you want?

129
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:02,320
I came today

130
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:04,040
just to find out some things.

131
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:07,180
About Yao Shengsheng.

132
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:41,800
Turn around.

133
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,680
She has a pea-sized scar on her back.

134
00:08:00,280 --> 00:08:02,010
I stabbed her when I was little.

135
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:18,580
What are you doing?

136
00:08:21,520 --> 00:08:22,600
What are you doing?

137
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:26,440
I should be asking you.

138
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:28,440
Why are you impersonating Yao Shengsheng?
